summaries.short: Merche is delighted by Angel's arrival, but as an ominous fog fills the village, the townspeople grow increasingly restless.
summaries.full: Angel arrives in Pedraza with a sinister plan and enlists Merche to do his bidding. As an ominous fog fills the streets, the townspeople grow increasingly restless. Meanwhile, Laguna finds himself at odds with the federal agents, Paco falls mysteriously ill, and Elena and Father Vergara rush to get home before it's too late.

summaries.short: Season finale. Elena, Paco, and Father Vergara fight to free their people from the spell of the Black Circle.
summaries.full: Season finale. Elena, Paco, and Father Vergara take shelter in an abandoned wine cellar as they fight to free the people of the Pedraza from the spell of the Black Circle. While Angel prepares the town for Santoro’s fateful arrival, Merche’s allegiances remain to be seen.

summaries.short: Father Vergara escapes to a warzone, Elena and Roque elope to Paris, Paco and Merche fall out, and federal agents descend on Pedraza.
summaries.full: While Father Vergara seeks refuge from Santoro in Aleppo, he ventures into the dream world to contact Elena, who's eloped to Paris with Roque. Meanwhile, in Pedraza, marital tensions between Paco and Merche reach a boiling point, and federal agents descend on the town to take matters into their own hands.

summaries.short: Elena and Mario's reunion sends the village reeling, while Santoro and Sandro each appeal to Father Vergara's better nature.
summaries.full: The village is further undone by Mario's return, sending Paco on an urgent quest for answers. As Sandro and Santoro each appeal to Father Vergara's better nature, the hunt for the final coin puts Elena in greater danger than ever before.

summaries.short: While old acquaintances greet Father Vergara in Rome, Paco fights to keep Elena in Pedraza.
summaries.full: Old acquaintances Sandro and Santoro delight in Father Vergara's return to Rome. Meanwhile, in Pedraza, the townspeople struggle to make amends with an embittered Elena as Paco fights to keep her close.
